不能和当下的新酒店比较
但是老式酒店就是很舒服', '2023-08-15', 3, '[''房间设施'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234512000bww7xrv2EBD_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234b12000bww6b38DE14_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235812000bww127803ED_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235512000bwwam92D8FC_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '位置很好，花园很漂亮，大堂很辉煌！人流很大！早餐还可以。但房间设施真的老旧，空调', '位置很好，花园很漂亮，大堂很辉煌！人流很大！早餐还可以。但房间设施真的老旧，空调声音很大，性价比低。空调不开潮湿，因为卫生间是开放的！与五星级不太匹配。', '2023-05-04', 4, '[''房间设施'', ''性价比'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230112000b5nhzg925E1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231v12000b5nj8fe1AB5_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230k12000b5nhf6f897B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230r12000b5ng4pmF51C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231c12000b5nbka6F37E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236512000b5nfultE223_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231v12000b5n8mal4CBB_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '非常非常的满意！前台的Tony小哥哥人也特别好！给我们升级了套房还送了我们两朵小', '非常非常的满意！前台的Tony小哥哥人也特别好！给我们升级了套房还送了我们两朵小花花~', '2023-07-16', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232412000bo8vypg1C02_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234j12000bo8wuku41E0_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231612000bo8xc325915_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '房间干净，环境优美。', '房间干净，环境优美。', '2023-09-02', 5, '[''卫生状况'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233512000c206myj3CAC_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230312000c206yrx6749_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230j12000c206vupCA7D_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.png\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '酒店环境更方面都很好，人也很多，小朋友早餐198一位，进去就喝了一碗稀饭哈哈哈', '酒店环境更方面都很好，人也很多，小朋友早餐198一位，进去就喝了一碗稀饭哈哈哈', '2023-07-03', 5, '[''餐饮设施'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235m12000bk7jlxp1E45_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '广州的花园酒店、白天鹅宾馆、白云宾馆一直是我这个五十多岁人心中的白月光，此次去广', '广州的花园酒店、白天鹅宾馆、白云宾馆一直是我这个五十多岁人心中的白月光，此次去广州旅游选择了花园酒店，原因有三：一、酒店门口即是地铁站，去景点、去机场在地面交通拥堵的情况下都能坐地铁到达；二、酒店内有博物馆，自带博物馆的酒店国内真的不多，闲暇之余参观一下，增长些知识也是件好事；三：酒店地处繁华地段，附近吃、喝、玩、乐非常方便。
下了出租，走进大堂的一刻，?一幅硕大的壁画映入眼帘，用金璧辉??来形容此画一点也不夸张，据说此画用了二公斤黄金-奢华！预定了二间房，因一间房仍在打扫中，前台竟然很客气地把房间升了级，升到了套房，而且，还贴心地提醒了一下：窗外正在进行地铁施工，有可能影响睡眠。第二天退房人又较多，在排队时有个女主管上来询问，当得知我们未使用房内任何物品后，就马上收了房卡退了房。从入住到退房，花园人的服务态度一流，若以后再来广州，花园将是我不二之选，还会再入住。谢谢！', '2023-04-18', 5, '[''交通便利性'', ''前台服务'', ''退房/入住效率'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236z12000aziqdgiF129_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230q12000azil3jhFB2B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231512000aziw1ec6764_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233m12000azj4y4sFD01_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235i12000azj1yyj0C2D_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231612000aziyi4vA2E2_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '行政酒廊很好，', '行政酒廊很好，', '2023-09-10', 5, '[''餐饮设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233z12000c3qi2qdB937_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '出行便利无论是地铁和出租方便出行，环境很好', '出行便利无论是地铁和出租方便出行，环境很好', '2023-08-10', 5, '[''交通便利性'', ''周边配套'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236h12000bvhojhk5DC7_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '赶上活动住的红棉双床房，各方面环境让人感觉宾至如归，健身房，游泳池一应俱全，四楼', '赶上活动住的红棉双床房，各方面环境让人感觉宾至如归，健身房，游泳池一应俱全，四楼的酒店博物馆亦是令人大开眼界，了解到花园酒店和整个行业的前世今生。前台“洪小姐”还热情的升级了房型，耐心解答了提出的问题，并且送了入住前点心，“洪小姐”大方得体，服务周到，简直就是花园酒店的一个缩影，总之这是一次非常令人满意的体验。', '2023-09-14', 5, '[''公共设施'', ''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231t12000c4rcnn1969D_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236j12000c4rco2s5D2C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230j12000c4rcmss8D69_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230212000c4rcnc261B1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '这次入住广州花园酒店，体验超棒！特别要夸夸办理入住的前厅部吴灵伶Lavinia ', '这次入住广州花园酒店，体验超棒！特别要夸夸办理入住的前厅部吴灵伶Lavinia 和退房的Betty，她们热情似火，笑容极具感染力，服务更是无可挑剔，专业又贴心。房间打扫得一尘不染，设施设备也一应俱全，方方面面都让人舒心，下次还来！', '2025-03-21', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''客房服务'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234h12000j7y55yv00DC_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233x12000j7z99qs550D_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230p12000j7y323wB441_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230w12000j7wvjry5F00_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '超级满意！！再次来住！！', '超级满意！！再次来住！！', '2023-08-26', 5, '[''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233j12000c0b2td3986F_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '入住广州花园酒店一进门被酒店的各项服务惊到了。位置好、环境好、软件服务好是名副其', '入住广州花园酒店一进门被酒店的各项服务惊到了。位置好、环境好、软件服务好是名副其实的花园酒店。特别办入住的小姐姐（好像是姓梁）一直面带微笑非常专业礼貌看我们老两口带了孩子还帮我们升级了房间，给我们提供各种方便入住3天2晚体验感超棒。会推荐朋友来体验超五星服务。', '2023-11-19', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236412000clnwi1v5193_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236t12000clns9raB400_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231012000clnw5y2DC3D_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0237212000clnos7iCB79_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230512000clnrb6782C1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233v12000clnq6h43180_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232t12000clnw5ym4058_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233u12000clnz5fu4BCF_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231p12000clnzepf9197_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '很漂亮的酒店～～', '很漂亮的酒店～～', '2023-09-05', 5, '[''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235e12000c2l4uf57893_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231g12000c2lal3l0670_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234612000c2l8tzc7E70_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235f12000c2lh91gC3A4_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233812000c2lal3pFBCF_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '宾客服务的kristy和rain小姐姐的服务都超级好，这家酒店无论是特色还是舒适', '宾客服务的kristy和rain小姐姐的服务都超级好，这家酒店无论是特色还是舒适度，都获得了我们全家人一致的高度评价。还没退房就已经计划好了，下次想继续来入住。', '2023-09-23', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236a12000c7zhoswF896_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230n12000c7zk99xEAD8_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234112000c7zer1z60EB_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232312000c7zdh2325B0_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '房间太小了 洗澡和厕所共用一扇拖拉门', '房间太小了 洗澡和厕所共用一扇拖拉门', '2023-08-16', 4, '[''房间设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236x12000bx809ne0702_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '酒店环境不错，服务态度好，周边好吃的也多，交通出行方便，推荐', '酒店环境不错，服务态度好，周边好吃的也多，交通出行方便，推荐', '2023-07-16', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''周边配套'', ''交通便利性'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234i12000bo7pyf02A07_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231u12000bo7ulnrB2C1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233q12000bo7qsic6523_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '贝聿铭设计的酒店，名副其实的花园酒店，后花园很漂亮，大小瀑布、锦鲤漫游，花团锦簇', '贝聿铭设计的酒店，名副其实的花园酒店，后花园很漂亮，大小瀑布、锦鲤漫游，花团锦簇，是休闲拍照好去处；酒店赠送的胶囊咖啡也好喝！', '2023-06-08', 5, '[''公共设施'', ''餐饮设施'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232m12000bdlqlxgCA1B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230g12000bdlukrs2C02_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233112000bdlsopb4428_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '环境很好 服务员热情，卫生级别高，四楼博物馆值得一看', '环境很好 服务员热情，卫生级别高，四楼博物馆值得一看', '2023-07-24', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''前台服务'', ''卫生状况'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231t12000bqg3ans098E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234u12000bqg3gjp59A6_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230m12000bqg3f9935A3_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '非常满意的一次商务旅途，花园酒店不愧是广州独有的很有历史沉淀的园林史酒店，环境一', '非常满意的一次商务旅途，花园酒店不愧是广州独有的很有历史沉淀的园林史酒店，环境一流，服务周到，特别是给我办入前厅部副经理吴灵伶 Lavinia，人美心善，服务态度特别好。园林里面有瀑布，有酒吧，特别适合商务洽谈，下次还会再入住的', '2024-09-02', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''前台服务'', ''公共设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236o12000fcmmw9v3D0D_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.png\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '酒店的环境很好，chloe和rainey服务非常nice', '酒店的环境很好，chloe和rainey服务非常nice', '2023-07-16', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234y12000bo4puot3884_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', 'Kamille,rain的服务很棒，送了小礼品很喜欢，环境很好～服务很贴心，下次', 'Kamille,rain的服务很棒，送了小礼品很喜欢，环境很好～服务很贴心，下次还来～卫生很好，设施齐全', '2023-06-01', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''卫生状况'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231b12000bc26jwt6D82_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231812000bc1tl3d9240_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234v12000bc26qpuF887_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232412000bc2448u663E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '服务很好呢，临走送了伴手礼，很香', '服务很好呢，临走送了伴手礼，很香', '2023-08-14', 5, '[''前台服务'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234t12000bwmvq1jE62C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236012000bwn3fk0B1E9_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '酒店很适合度假 服务好 环境好', '酒店很适合度假 服务好 环境好', '2023-08-10', 5, '[''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230x12000bvmc9bs27C3_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232j12000bvmd2pu4ABA_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234412000bvm97r602C1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '超级好评，帮我免费升级了套房，环境舒适高级，很有质感，酒店服务满分，走时还送了欧', '超级好评，帮我免费升级了套房，环境舒适高级，很有质感，酒店服务满分，走时还送了欧舒丹礼盒。满分体验。', '2023-06-01', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''前台服务'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232612000bc38tr4EDD7_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230i12000bc3i5hk078F_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231912000bc36cdrF03C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234u12000bc3hw3x04FC_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234q12000bc38r2c18BB_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '很有特色的酒店，一楼有点像购物中心，花园比我想的大，酒店里面还有博物馆可以看看，', '很有特色的酒店，一楼有点像购物中心，花园比我想的大，酒店里面还有博物馆可以看看，服务也很友善，正赶上中秋节大堂的rain姐姐还送了一盒月饼??，感谢??????', '2023-09-29', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''公共设施'', ''前台服务'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235012000ca4azr6B060_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236112000ca4ad5p7034_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234b12000ca46w5eCCE5_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232812000ca488scA12E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236v12000ca4c5ni31B0_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230k12000ca4j3a3BADC_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '中秋假期订了广州老牌的花园酒店，在一众涨价的各大五星酒店面前性价比很高。红棉大床', '中秋假期订了广州老牌的花园酒店，在一众涨价的各大五星酒店面前性价比很高。红棉大床房很大，有客厅和卧室有效隔开，内部装潢历久弥新，只有历史的厚重感没有陈旧过时的感觉。服务也很好，特别是Tia小姐姐很贴心的送了月饼，好评！下次还会推荐亲朋好友来住～', '2024-09-18', 5, '[''性价比'', ''房间设施'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231i12000fmct7yp36D3_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234012000fmcjc66060E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232g12000fmcz9hx0872_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '入住时前台Billy的接待自信大方，不仅赠送了小礼物和升级了房型，还介绍了酒店各', '入住时前台Billy的接待自信大方，不仅赠送了小礼物和升级了房型，还介绍了酒店各个区域及预约方式。
因酒店毕竟时间太长了房间设备比较陈旧可以理解，但也都是好用的。来住这家酒店最主要的目的是去博物馆，对酒店文化一直很感兴趣，博物馆的确各个细节也做的很好，希望花园酒店可以把博物馆的内容出一套书，对酒店爱好者来说会很有意义。
一楼瀑布餐厅的服务也很贴心，体验感很好。
唯一希望改善的是客房餐饮部的出品，点了白葡萄酒但送来时既没有冰桶，酒杯虽是冰过的但是上面擦不掉的水渍还是很影响心情，再次送来的干净杯子就不是白酒杯了……', '2023-05-30', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''餐饮设施'', ''房间设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233b12000bbi8poxC5F8_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235e12000bbi1y6nCA70_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '很棒的酒店！已经多次入住了！', '很棒的酒店！已经多次入住了！', '2023-08-15', 5, '[''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236r12000bwxp4c8A228_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234512000bwxwmz4A8AA_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232g12000bwxu9vw0352_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233s12000bwxo0jv5AB7_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '多次入住了，到广州必选！美美哒瀑布餐厅，丰盛的早餐，老客户给升级套间，棒棒哒！贵', '多次入住了，到广州必选！美美哒瀑布餐厅，丰盛的早餐，老客户给升级套间，棒棒哒！贵宾专享行政酒廊，推荐！', '2023-06-12', 5, '[''餐饮设施'', ''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231m12000befbwnr2573_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234712000befi1zu5D4C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232n12000bef7x7u8196_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232x12000bef91pq0DBA_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230u12000befck0zA116_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233d12000befhj5c6578_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236912000befira6211B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230d12000befbdtrA9BB_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230y12000befisedDB8B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '后花园好漂亮', '后花园好漂亮', '2023-08-26', 5, '[''景观/朝向'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231e12000c0d8dx6053F_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232b12000c0d9ijf4DD3_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '环境优美，服务周到。有品质、有文化的酒店。', '环境优美，服务周到。有品质、有文化的酒店。', '2023-07-23', 5, '[''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235z12000bq409khD62E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231312000bq416eb01B4_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0237112000bq4371v1380_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235n12000bq43jwn6D9F_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232z12000bq47swo0D7E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '服务很好，不过就是设施有点旧，跟不上潮流，没有充电头，还有厕所门好紧，有点推不动', '服务很好，不过就是设施有点旧，跟不上潮流，没有充电头，还有厕所门好紧，有点推不动?????♀?，但接待员好好，抵回，还送了五百现金，这是意外惊喜。', '2023-04-21', 4, '[''房间设施'', ''前台服务'', ''性价比'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230r2215eqeeytyoC6A5_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '之前来广州都是首选花园酒店，這次入住真的很失望，住两晚换了三次房间！', '之前来广州都是首选花园酒店，這次入住真的很失望，住两晚换了三次房间！
定的无烟房被分派了有烟房，一进门就是扑鼻的烟味。和前台反应换到了无烟房，但房间打扫完全不到位，卫生间还留有之前住客的使用痕迹，再次下楼和反应，接待的礼仪小姐姐还是很不错！立即安排换房又做了升级。 
换到了行政套房房间整体都还不错，但一开空调房间的出风口就是一股下水道酸臭味漂出来，可惜当晚没房可换了，只能让阿姨拿了空气清新剂和空气净化器先解决一下。
 
事后得知据说16层以上才是新装修的，后续要入住的尽量选高楼层的吧！', '2023-04-15', 3, '[''房间设施'', ''前台服务'', ''卫生状况'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232912000ayae91q21D2_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '出行首先广州花园酒店，各方面服务都非常赞无论是前台接待还是客房餐厅都挑不出一丁点', '出行首先广州花园酒店，各方面服务都非常赞无论是前台接待还是客房餐厅都挑不出一丁点毛病，本来是想住一晚办完事就走，前台接待工作人员周到的服务，温暖到了我，毫不犹豫又延住一晚，酒店位置很好对面商城6楼有一家1935年开业的老店特别赞，下次来广州还会选择花园酒店。', '2023-03-07', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'', ''周边配套'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234412000aqz52jnEAF7_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231w12000aqz562r0083_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231112000aqz562zAC45_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236312000aqz587084EB_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234512000aqz53bs2B85_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232h12000aqz53cm3E7B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235612000aqz53cxA6DF_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230y12000aqz54ua21EF_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234f12000aqz587vF946_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '环境很棒，很喜欢，kamille服务很棒!下次还会过来。', '环境很棒，很喜欢，kamille服务很棒!下次还会过来。', '2023-07-02', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''前台服务'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236312000bjys4i87D5C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234e12000bjyrf5g2984_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236o12000bjysy5vA413_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234c12000bjyotyb4D7B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232k12000bjyqcebEAA5_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235p12000bjyyhst83BD_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '挺好的一次入住体验，酒店位于市中心，离地铁站很近，叫车也很方便，前台的Betty', '挺好的一次入住体验，酒店位于市中心，离地铁站很近，叫车也很方便，前台的Betty人很nice，给升级了房间，使得这次入住更加愉快。', '2023-12-18', 5, '[''交通便利性'', ''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233q12000cra1luu5CD5_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231812000cr9xegk9919_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236g12000cra26d3DDF7_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235x12000cra5yda2B12_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '作为一家很有历史的酒店，各项设施还是很不错的。后花园很漂亮，很多网红拍照。酒店早', '作为一家很有历史的酒店，各项设施还是很不错的。后花园很漂亮，很多网红拍照。酒店早餐也不错。服务很好，给小姐姐krysty点赞。', '2023-05-03', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''餐饮设施'', ''公共设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233i12000b5ak5p9A6DE_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231p12000b5a061c4756_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '酒店交通方便，环境也很棒，服务也好,nice.', '酒店交通方便，环境也很棒，服务也好,nice.', '2023-07-11', 5, '[''交通便利性'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235112000bmo8o2t43C4_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '第二天还是选择住在花园酒店，因为赶时间就直接把房卡给到迎宾小姐姐续房了！真的满分', '第二天还是选择住在花园酒店，因为赶时间就直接把房卡给到迎宾小姐姐续房了！真的满分服务，回来直接到前台拿上饭卡又可以回房间里了，服务还是一如既往的好！
设施：虽然稍微旧了一点，但是品质质感都是满满的赞！床品也还挺舒适的，酒店的水压是我住过这么多酒店以来水压最大的一个，出热水很快且水量很大，洗澡还是很爽的！
晚上去花园逛了逛，小桥流水体现的淋漓尽致，不愧是大师手笔，有瀑布有锦鲤！酒店的酒吧应该也还不错，下次可以去试试', '2023-03-06', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''房间设施'', ''公共设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0237312000aqt0xknBA63_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230i12000aqt6ju11812_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230q12000aqt5b5f1D60_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230e12000aqt5ln493CC_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233r12000aqszkfe20F8_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233312000aqt33hj5818_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234612000aqt6wc5EBF2_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235t12000aqszloc3C08_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '非常好，家人也觉得很棒，行政酒廊的工作人员都很热情，专业，印度籍的Carrie ', '非常好，家人也觉得很棒，行政酒廊的工作人员都很热情，专业，印度籍的Carrie 中文说的很好，跟小孩互动。', '2023-05-15', 5, '[''餐饮设施'', ''前台服务'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231k12000b82711oE870_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236y12000b8269sxD749_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230w12000b81vxbuE780_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230912000b82aouv0147_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230b12000b82e5zt53D0_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '这二十年来 一直选择花园酒店 地理位置优越 这次依然选择酒店 首先感谢billy', '这二十年来 一直选择花园酒店 地理位置优越 这次依然选择酒店 首先感谢billy 非常有礼貌 很耐心的男士 让我们一开始就以非常愉快的心情入住酒店 其次感谢酒店各部门的工作人员 我有一件衣服落在酒店 酒店联系我 并寄回给我 非常感谢 花园酒店是我去广州不变的选择 感谢??', '2023-09-25', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'', ''客房服务'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232q12000c8ix7b76840_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", 