.c-ctrip.com/images/0231o12000b564rm9312A_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235s12000b5618nlA1FD_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231412000b55xa3tB52D_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234q12000b563mf237A6_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234r12000b56ftnqE441_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233w12000b562t30F77E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '服务：满意', '服务：满意
